<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Singapore Honeymoon</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero Banner -->
  <section class="country-hero-honey" style="background: url('/img/pexels-photo-777059.jpeg');">
    <h1>Singapore Honeymoon</h1>
    <p>Urban sophistication, island escapes, and unforgettable nights</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Description -->
  <section class="country-description-honey">
    <p>
      Singapore blends culture, elegance, and tropical charm into one romantic escape. From gardens in the sky to luxurious waterfront dinners, it's the perfect destination for couples seeking both excitement and intimacy. Celebrate your honeymoon in one of Asia’s cleanest, safest, and most scenic cities.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Attractions -->
  <section class="attractions-honey">
    <h2>Most Popular Honeymoon Places in Singapore</h2>
    <div class="attraction-grid-honey">

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/9b7ef100bfac0c44a2eb34dd61364ac7.jpg" alt="Marina Bay Sands">
        <h3>Marina Bay Sands</h3>
        <p>Stay or visit this iconic resort with a rooftop infinity pool, luxury shopping, and panoramic skyline views. Perfect for a honeymoon photo moment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/1e99139da3405502e3a30b32e660f62d.jpg" alt="Gardens by the Bay">
        <h3>Gardens by the Bay</h3>
        <p>Wander through floral domes and towering supertrees that light up the night. A magical garden experience for couples.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/eedc06158ad086aa5be605151ac45315.jpg" alt="Sentosa Island">
        <h3>Sentosa Island</h3>
        <p>A romantic island escape just minutes from the city. Relax on white sand beaches, enjoy luxury spas, or take a cable car ride at sunset.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/eeb2c287194d06c546a321c980df2137.jpg" alt="Clarke Quay">
        <h3>Clarke Quay</h3>
        <p>Singapore’s riverside nightlife hub. Dine by the water, dance the night away, or hop on a romantic river cruise.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/ec136522dd81d5dc721211c6b7d20bbc.jpg" alt="Singapore Botanic Gardens">
        <h3>Botanic Gardens</h3>
        <p>A UNESCO World Heritage Site. Perfect for morning strolls, picnics, and couple photos in the orchid garden.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/14335051179f9bc64ef4d4f0aee2d54e.jpg" alt="Jewel Changi Airport">
        <h3>Jewel at Changi</h3>
        <p>Not just an airport. It's a honeymoon stop with a lush indoor forest, the world’s tallest indoor waterfall, and stylish shops.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Hotels -->
  <section class="hotels-honey">
    <h2>Romantic Stays in Singapore</h2>
    <div class="hotel-grid-honey">

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/23befd381f6c9e9687abe6b1fae05316.jpg" alt="Raffles Singapore">
        <h3>Raffles Singapore</h3>
        <p>A legendary colonial-style hotel offering luxury suites, tranquil courtyards, and timeless romantic charm.</p>
        <a href="https://www.rafflessingapore.com/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/8e9d30fb60ed318d722c56b418022dc4.jpg" alt="Marina Bay Sands Hotel">
        <h3>Marina Bay Sands</h3>
        <p>One of the world’s most iconic honeymoon hotels with an infinity pool overlooking the skyline and unforgettable evening ambiance.</p>
        <a href="https://www.marinabaysands.com/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/99a9d34b870c905f8a4d87319f9410ab.jpg" alt="Capella Singapore">
        <h3>Capella Singapore</h3>
        <p>A tranquil and luxurious retreat on Sentosa Island with spacious villas, rainforest views, and world-class spa experiences.</p>
        <a href="https://www.capellahotels.com/en/capella-singapore" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/aa4741cf20b901c5fbe0300869b099f3.jpg" alt="The Fullerton Hotel">
        <h3>The Fullerton Hotel</h3>
        <p>A romantic neoclassical icon by the riverfront, offering elegant rooms, rooftop views, and romantic dining experiences.</p>
        <a href="https://www.fullertonhotels.com/fullerton-hotel-singapore" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/f114a3fdbcae0ec150f997d3faf8047b.jpg" alt="Sofitel Sentosa">
        <h3>Sofitel Singapore Sentosa</h3>
        <p>Escape to this cliff-top hideaway with tropical gardens, couples' spa, and romantic vibes on every corner of Sentosa.</p>
        <a href="https://www.sofitel-singapore-sentosa.com/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/8bc3879fa93d072c57a2a5694189dd62.jpg" alt="The Clan Hotel Singapore">
        <h3>The Clan Hotel</h3>
        <p>A modern luxury hotel in the heart of the city with rooftop pools and cozy city-view rooms, perfect for couples who love convenience and style.</p>
        <a href="https://www.theclanhotel.com.sg/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
